oracle.pg.rdbms.index.jdbc.operators

Class FetchOnOpenJdbcIndexInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.store.DataInput
      • org.apache.lucene.store.IndexInput
        • oracle.pg.rdbms.index.jdbc.operators.FetchOnOpenJdbcIndexInput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Cloneable, JdbcIndexConfigurable

    public class FetchOnOpenJdbcIndexInput
extends org.apache.lucene.store.IndexInput
implements JdbcIndexConfigurable
    An Oracle extension of Compass FetchOnOpenJdbcIndexInput class. This class perform will read all the relevant data from the database when created an will cache it until it is closed.
